data.description: You're going to love these views enjoy this rare find Backed up to BLM!! If you are seeking a cozy rustic ranch, feel home this is it! right of pavement Located midway between Kingman, AZ and Henderson, NV near Hwy 93 in the Old Historic Mining town of Chloride, 3Bd, 1 BA + an upstairs loft, Wood beam ceilings + freestanding wood burning fireplace. very open floor plan with a great rustic feel. Alcove siding, Fully fenced land, bring the horses, goats, donkey etc! Detached oversized one car garage + RV PARKING DUAL GATES.
